      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and it\u2019s honestly been such a great car to own. It\u2019s in really wonderful shape and has been super reliable for me\u2014perfect for someone who wants a dependable vehicle that still looks and feels great on the road! It's ready for its next adventure, so feel free to reach out if you have any questions. I'd love to see it go to a good home!",
