    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sorted driver\u2019s example featuring the high-revving S54 inline-six engine equipped with individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. The critical dual-VANOS system has been serviced, and the rear subframe\u2014a known structural weak point\u2014has been proactively reinforced with plates. Power is managed through a tactile 6-speed manual transmission and a factory limited-slip differential. The chassis remains composed thanks to refreshed bushings and Bilstein B6 dampers. While the exterior shows minor stone chips consistent with spirited use, the drivetrain is dialed-in and offers exceptional throttle response and linear power delivery.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 13
    },
    {
