      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a prime example of dependable performance meeting everyday utility. Mechanically, it is in excellent shape; the engine purrs quietly, the transmission shifts seamlessly, and the brakes provide firm, responsive stopping power. We have kept a rigorous maintenance schedule, ensuring all fluids and filters were replaced on time. Visually, the car presents very well with a high-gloss finish, though a close inspection will reveal some minor road rash on the front bumper and a few small door dings that do not detract from its overall sharp appearance. The interior has been kept exceptionally clean, featuring supple seating with minimal wear and a fully functional dashboard where every button and dial works perfectly. It offers a smooth, rattle-free ride and is ready to hit the road immediately without any needed repairs.",
      "price": 34500.0,
